{"QUIZ":[{"def":"A riddle or obscure question; an enigma; a ridiculous hoax.","pos":""},{"def":"One who quizzes others; as, he is a great quiz.","pos":""}],"QUIZZER":[{"def":"One who quizzes; a quiz.","pos":""}],"QUIZZICAL":[{"def":"Relating to quizzing: given to quizzing; of the nature of a quiz; farcical; sportive.","pos":""}],"QUIZZISM":[{"def":"The act or habit of quizzing.","pos":""}]}